title: executable()
brief: Test whether a given path represents an executable.
seealso: is_directory, file_exists
version: 0.08
----

<p>This function tests whether the specified path is executable.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
if ( executable( "/usr/bin/imapsync" ) ) then
   <a href="/lua/msg.html">msg</a>( "We have imapsync installed" )
end
</pre>
